{"tid":10504,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"普巴：曼聯比人咀咒呀！！！！","createTime":"2016-11-29T03:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T03:39:02.000Z","uid":28394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3582ce60b53d8be7e9a2087ce497340f30b3cde3","tid":10504,"uid":28394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:31:36.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=bb3dd489\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯主場4連和，上場英超圍攻韋斯咸仍只賽和1:1，中場保羅普巴竟然歸咎於「紅魔」被詛咒。<br />\n<br />\n「我們真的要想想，自己是不是被詛咒了。不論是那一支球隊作客我們，我們都主宰了球賽，像之前的阿仙奴和上仗的韋斯咸。希望運氣將會逐場的改變。」今夏以破世界紀錄轉會費由祖雲達斯回歸曼聯的保羅普巴（Paul Pogba）表示。<br />\n<br />\n雖然如此，但這名法國國腳仍然對球隊充滿信心：「因為我們能夠創造出不少入球機會，勝利將會來臨，我對我的球隊十分有信心，只需要在一些細節上，再留意多一點就可以了。」<br />\n<br />\n普巴說的細節，其中一點就是防守。他說：「對韋斯咸我們有一個愚蠢的失球，對阿仙奴也一樣，這就是細節。我們愚蠢地失了分數，不過我有信心事情會好轉的。」"},{"pid":"fdff1c959405cfc33508b0e6ea8625ce8479bbe2","tid":10504,"uid":25019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/113632_64f6f33fd001d89e436aa1f0741ee148.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F113632_64f6f33fd001d89e436aa1f0741ee148.jpg&h=752c6ad1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8186d684b37c27fd2e950ef4b2f66e71aca92f9","tid":10504,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:37:36.000Z","msg":"妹下妹下"},{"pid":"4bcda366440f9329b67f52a0928f5ab2c16896dd","tid":10504,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:38:15.000Z","msg":"我咒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4bedb4e28f3c09f76008d48e1082e5c6eb1c12","tid":10504,"uid":4206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:38:59.000Z","msg":"洗咗成億<br />\n結果要靠運氣贏波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5756b0721d951a8c5a0872ab9d6e3613d2f9cdf","tid":10504,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:39:02.000Z","msg":"最衰d反曼<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}